title: Super bluetooth hacker
description:
Super Bluetooth Hacker - 2008
The Super Bluetooth Hack is for you to data from other phones via Bluetooth. Once connected to another phone via Bluetooth you can: - Read the messages - See the list of contacts - Change the profile - Make the phone rings while in silent mode - making downloads of ringtones (for your phone) - Restart the phone - Turn off the phone - Restore the values of origin - Change of touch Volume - And here comes the best "Do Links of another cell" among others
